   <p xml:id="8" begin="00:00:18.558" end="00:00:20.259">YOU WE NEED TO HAVE A </p>
   <p xml:id="9" begin="00:00:19.625" end="00:00:22.128">CONVERSATION ABOUT RACE.</p>
   <p xml:id="10" begin="00:00:20.393" end="00:00:24.197">AND WHENEVER YOU HEAR THAT, YOU </p>
