   <p xml:id="15" begin="00:00:29.869" end="00:00:32.605">AND THEY GET VAGUE.</p>
   <p xml:id="16" begin="00:00:30.703" end="00:00:33.506">YOU KNOW, WE HAVE TO HAVE A </p>
