   <p xml:id="18" begin="00:00:33.639" end="00:00:36.075">EACH OTHER.</p>
   <p xml:id="19" begin="00:00:34.607" end="00:00:38.177">I HAVE IDEA WHAT THAT MEANS.</p>
   <p xml:id="20" begin="00:00:36.209" end="00:00:39.145">WEVE BEEN HAVING ONE FOR 50 </p>
   <p xml:id="21" begin="00:00:38.311" end="00:00:40.746">YEARS IN THIS COUNTRY.</p>
