   <p xml:id="27" begin="00:00:47.787" end="00:00:49.522">NATIONAL DISCOURSE, ITS BEEN </p>
   <p xml:id="28" begin="00:00:49.355" end="00:00:50.623">RACE.</p>
   <p xml:id="29" begin="00:00:49.655" end="00:00:52.358">THE IDEA THAT WE HAVENT </p>
