   <p xml:id="32" begin="00:00:52.925" end="00:00:56.229">WHAT IS USUALLY IMPLIED IS THAT </p>
   <p xml:id="33" begin="00:00:54.627" end="00:00:57.964">WHITES OUGHT TO BE CONFESSING </p>
   <p xml:id="34" begin="00:00:56.362" end="00:00:59.265">THEIR RACISM AND THAT SHOULD BE </p>
