   <p xml:id="36" begin="00:00:59.398" end="00:01:03.636">I REFUSE TO ACCEPT THAT PREMISE.</p>
   <p xml:id="37" begin="00:01:01.834" end="00:01:05.171">I THINK IF YOU WANT TO HAVE AN </p>
